SuccessfulTargetSelection.Description: Successfully selected a target object within the response window

UnsuccessfulTargetSelection.Description: Selected a target not within the response window after an animation

TargetSelectionBeforeFirstAnim.Description: Target selected before the first animation begins

AdditionalTargetSelection.Description: Target selected after already being selected once during the current animation interval

TargetAnimWithoutSelection.Description: Target animation occured without a selection
